chap2.search.maze

Class AbstractSearchEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • chap2.search.maze.AbstractSearchEngine
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BreadthFirstSearchEngine, DepthFirstSearchEngine

    public class AbstractSearchEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    2D Maze Search. This abstract class contains common code and data that is required by both the depth first (uses a stack to to store moves) search class DepthFirstSearchEngine and the breadth first (uses a queue to store moves) search class BreadthFirstSearchEngine.
    Author:
    Rambod Rahmani <rambodrahmani@autistici.org>
